==描述==
屬下的植物是[[常綠|常綠]][[喬木|喬木]]<ref name=wa/>、[[灌木|灌木]]或[[攀緣植物|攀緣植物]]<ref name=haron>Haron, F. F., et al. (2013). [http://scialert.net/fulltext/?doi=jbs.2013.158.162 Bioassay-guided isolation of antifungal plumericin from ''Allamanda'' species (Apocynaceae).] ''Journal of Biological Sciences'' 13, 158-62.</ref>，有白色[[乳膠|乳膠]]。其果為[[離果|離果]]，當中有2至4粒籽<ref name=wa/>。

